headline: J.B. Hunt Transport Services, Inc. Announces Participation in Upcoming Investor Conferences
summary: LOWELL, Ark., May 02, 2025--J.B. Hunt Transport Services, Inc. (NASDAQ: JBHT) Executive Vice President of Sales and Marketing Spencer Frazier and Senior Vice President of Intermodal Pricing Stacey Griffin will address the Bank of America Industrials, Transportation and Airlines Key Leaders Conference in New York City, New York, at 11:05am EDT on Tuesday, May 13, 2025.
